      "beat_id": "B01",
      "act": "COLD OPEN",
      "estimated_duration_s": 11,
      "narration_text": "This is Liam, in for Bear. In the simplest crystal model, one free-electron energy is split into two at a special wave number. The missing energies between them are a band gap.",
