        "filled_by": "manim",
        "at": "2026-07-18T19:46:18"
      }
    },
    {
      "beat_id": "B10",
      "act": "THE EXAMPLE",
      "estimated_duration_s": 11,
      "narration_text": "Take a toy weak lattice with Fourier coefficient magnitude zero-point-five-five electron-volts. The model predicts a one-point-one electron-volt gap. That arithmetic is illustrative; it is not a band-structure calculation for silicon.",
